OL,6,FAlmost half of people are dipping into
OL,7,Ftheir savings ` on average three times
OL,8,Fa month ` to cover everyday costs, a
OL,9,Fsurvey suggests.
OL,11,FThis is despite 61% of people feeling
OL,12,Fmore optimistic about their finances
OL,13,Fcompared to this time last year, with
OL,14,Fone in three (39%) feeling more
OL,15,Fpessimistic, according to Compare the
OL,16,FMarket's last Household Financial
OL,17,FConfidence Tracker.
