OL,6,FThree quarters (76%) feel confident
OL,7,Fabout being able to manage and pay
OL,8,Ftheir household bills in the coming
OL,9,Fmonths.
OL,11,FHowever, when asked how often people
OL,12,Fare needing to dip into their monthly
OL,13,Fsavings to afford everyday living
OL,14,Fcosts, 45% admit they do so at least
OL,15,Fonce a month and 21% need to at least
OL,16,Fonce a week.
