OL,6,FAndy Hancock, chief growth officer at
OL,7,FCompare the Market, said: "It is
OL,8,Fencouraging that people are seemingly
OL,9,Fconfident about their ability to
OL,10,Fmanage and pay their everyday bills in
OL,11,Fthe summer months ahead, signalling a
OL,12,Fpositive outlook on the consistency
OL,13,Fand reliability of their financial
OL,14,Fsituations.
